column5: It's that time of year again, at 4:30 tomorrow morning I'm on the road heading for the French river. I'll be gone for a week of fresh air and relaxation. Hope to bring back some good fish stories and a few pictures to go along with them. See you all soon.  P.S.- ccmtcanada I got your new entry and will post it when I get home I gotta finish packing and get to sleep.
Have a great trip taper!!!  No worries about the entry...it only adds half an inch to our totals....LOL
Got get 'em taper.  I'm heading that way for a couple weeks in mid-September.   Save one or two for me.
